title: The 2022 “My Guys” Episode! - Fantasy Football Podcast for 8/18
description:
On today’s fantasy football podcast, it’s the annual “MY GUYS” episode! Andy, Mike, and Jason each give three players they aren’t leaving fantasy football drafts without! Plus, the latest edition of “Best Ball Breakdown” presented by Underdog Fantasy. Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for August 18th, 2022.

The 2022 Ultimate Draft Kit and Draft Analyzer are available NOW
